import React from "react"; import ReactDOM from "react-dom"; import './index.css' let heading = { color: '#fa9191', textAlign: 'center', textTransform: 'capitalize', fontWeight: 'bold' } let hour = new Date().getHours() console.log(hour) let greet = hour ReactDOM.render( <>
Hello Sir,
{greet}
, document.getElementById("root") )
